publication.description: An interactive journey journal for professional hairstylists featuring 16 comprehensive chapters, quizzes, worksheets, and practical strategies for building a successful, conscious hairstyling practice. Includes business development, networking, sustainability, and personal growth content with embedded fonts and professional design elements.
